txt.en: 'A powerful Angmarim sorcerer has journeyed to Evendim. Perhaps he has come to lead an attack upon Annúminas? One thing is for certain: Súnath, this powerful man of Angmar, must be dealt with.'
Brangil can be found in Tinnudir.\n\nYou should speak with Brangil.
The nefarious forces of Angmar travel to Evendim in search of powerful artifacts, including Súnath, who commands forces within Annúminas.
Súnath can be found somewhere in Evendim.\n\nYou should defeat Súnath.
'We Rangers thank you for your efforts. May we soon chase the last of the Angmarim out of Annúminas and reseal the city's ancient tombs.'
